  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f 18 \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Man arrested with 18 stolen bicycles in Batticaloa",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Divisional Headquarters Police said that on Thursday 07th, a person from Katankudi who had stolen two-wheelers in Batticaloa city was arrested and 18 stolen two-wheelers were recovered.",
        "When a person stole a washing machine parked in front of a private company in Madu on the day of the incident, the employees of the private company caught the thief and handed them over to the police.",
        "After this, Crime Prevention Division Officer-in-Charge Sub-Inspector M.G.B.M.M. According to the investigation conducted by the police led by Yesuli, he used to travel by bus from Kathankudi every day to Madu Nagar and stole two-wheelers parked on the streets there and sold them in Kathankudi area for Rs 17,000 to Rs 25,000.",
        "Preliminary investigation by the police has revealed that some of the bikes were sold as parts and some of them were stolen and sold for money while addicted to drugs.",
        "The police said that 18 stolen and sold bicycles have been recovered and steps have been taken to produce the said person in court on 08th Friday and the people who stole the bicycles can go to the police station and identify the bicycles and get them."
      ],
